    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a standard action you can fire a shimmering ray at any foe within 30 feet as a ranged touch attack. The ray causes creatures to be&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/conditions#TOC-Blinded\" rel=\"nofollow\">blinded</a>&nbsp;for 1 round. Creatures with more Hit Dice than your wizard level are&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/conditions#TOC-Dazzled\" rel=\"nofollow\">dazzled</a>&nbsp;for 1 round instead. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Intelligence-Int-\" rel=\"nofollow\">Intelligence</a>&nbsp;modifier.</p>"
